stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Available
    
    Available --> Activated: User accepts
    Activated --> InProgress: Work begins
    InProgress --> ProgressUpdated: Milestone reached
    ProgressUpdated --> InProgress: Continue
    InProgress --> Completed: All requirements met
    Completed --> Rewarded: Distribute rewards
    Rewarded --> Shared: Optional sharing
    Shared --> [*]
    
    InProgress --> Failed: Time expired
    Failed --> Available: Reset
    InProgress --> Abandoned: User cancels
    Abandoned --> Available: Reset
    
    note right of Activated
        Challenge Types:
        - Time-based (24h, 7d)
        - Skill-based (Debugging)
        - Collaborative (Team)
        - Competitive (Leaderboard)
    end note
    
    note right of Rewarded
        Reward Types:
        - XP Points (100-10,000)
        - Badges (Bronze-Platinum)
        - Credits (For marketplace)
        - Early Access (Features)
        - Physical Merch
    end note